@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> .
@prefix sssom: <https://w3id.org/sssom/schema/> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix xwkont-source-term: <https://w3id.org/xwkont/source-term#> .

<https://w3id.org/xwkont/id#mapping:continuous-discrete:001> a sssom:Mapping ;
    rdfs:comment "Split 2026-07-08 (session-052) from a single row that had lumped GFO's Continuous/Discrete/Discrete_presential family against a placeholder 'ContinuousDiscrete' candidate that predated core.ttl's actual paired-split placement (session-050). GFO directly reifies `Continuous` as the `Individual`-side complement of `Discrete`, exactly the concept `xwkont-core:Continuous` is tracking."@en ;
    sssom:confidence 1e+00 ;
    sssom:mapping_justification "semapv:ManualMappingCuration" ;
    sssom:object_id xwkont-source-term:xwkont-core-Continuous ;
    sssom:predicate_id skos:exactMatch ;
    sssom:subject_id xwkont-source-term:GFO-Continuous .

<https://w3id.org/xwkont/id#mapping:continuous-discrete:002> a sssom:Mapping ;
    rdfs:comment "Split 2026-07-08 (session-052) from the same original row as `mapping-001`. GFO directly reifies `Discrete` under `Individual`, exactly the concept `xwkont-core:Discrete` is tracking; `Discrete_presential` is a further presential-side specialization of `Discrete`, not a separate axis."@en ;
    sssom:confidence 1e+00 ;
    sssom:mapping_justification "semapv:ManualMappingCuration" ;
    sssom:object_id xwkont-source-term:xwkont-core-Discrete ;
    sssom:predicate_id skos:exactMatch ;
    sssom:subject_id xwkont-source-term:GFO-Discrete_Discrete_presential .

<https://w3id.org/xwkont/id#mapping:continuous-discrete:008> a sssom:Mapping ;
    rdfs:comment "Reified hit, but activity-specific and one-sided; not enough to establish a general correspondence. TUpper's `atomic` is discrete-side vocabulary only -- unlike the other absence rows, this one is not axis-wide, so it maps against `xwkont-core:Discrete` alone, not the full `Continuous`/`Discrete` pair."@en ;
    sssom:confidence 2e-01 ;
    sssom:mapping_justification "semapv:ManualMappingCuration" ;
    sssom:object_id xwkont-source-term:TUpper-atomic ;
    sssom:subject_id xwkont-source-term:xwkont-core-Discrete .

xwkont-source-term:GFO-Continuous rdfs:label "Continuous"@en ;
    dcterms:source "GFO" .

xwkont-source-term:GFO-Discrete_Discrete_presential rdfs:label "Discrete / Discrete_presential"@en ;
    dcterms:source "GFO" .

xwkont-source-term:TUpper-atomic rdfs:label "atomic"@en ;
    dcterms:source "TUpper" .

xwkont-source-term:xwkont-core-Continuous rdfs:label "Continuous"@en ;
    dcterms:source "xwkont-core" .

xwkont-source-term:xwkont-core-Discrete rdfs:label "Discrete"@en ;
    dcterms:source "xwkont-core" .

